item.title: CVE-2023-6638|2024-08-02T08:35:14.859Z -- gutengeek -- gg%20woo%20feed%20for%20woocommerce%20shopping%20feed%20on%20google%20facebook%20and%20other%20channels
item.description: The GTG Product Feed for Shopping plugin for WordPress is vulnerable to unauthorized modification of data due to a missing capability check on the 'update_settings' function in versions up to, and including, 1.2.4. This makes it possible for unauthenticated attackers to update plugin settings.
